ADDITIONAL ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT (permitted under GPL-3.0 §7)
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
As an additional requirement under GPL-3.0 section 7(b), any covered work
that is publicly distributed (e.g. published on a server, Modrinth, Hangar,
SpigotMC, or any other platform) MUST display clear and visible credit to the
original project in ALL of the following locations:

  1. IN-GAME — /bitemfilter about (or equivalent) must include the line:
       "Based on bitemfilter by blackowlzz — https://modrinth.com/plugin/bitemfilter"

  2. REPOSITORY / DOCS — The public README must contain a "Credits" section
     that names the original project and links to this repository.

  3. DISTRIBUTION PAGE — Any store page, Modrinth listing, forum post, or
     website promoting the fork must mention bitemfilter as the original work.

